{"id": "ChIJr5hMNKF-hYARxmkk-5t0SzE", "rating": 4.8, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 3923, "displayName": {"text": "Cheese Board Collective Pizzeria", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "A pizzeria, bakery & cheese shop, this spot serves 1 style of veggie pizza per day & limited seats.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJr5hMNKF-hYARxmkk-5t0SzE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SV1JGZzRSV2N5VmxORFZ6RnRRMUJaYjJSRVNtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Popped in on April 30 and tried the mushroom pizza + salad. They do a different vegan pizza every day. As a huge meat lover, I was surprised by how much I liked the mushroom one. The staff were super sweet and even gave me an extra slice! Also, the salad was so fresh, and that green sauce is so good that I bought a small tub to take home.\n\nLove that it’s a worker-owned co-op with a classic Berkeley feel. Their website is actually super helpful too. You can check the daily pizza/bakery menu and live music schedule before you go.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Popped in on April 30 and tried the mushroom pizza + salad. They do a different vegan pizza every day. As a huge meat lover, I was surprised by how much I liked the mushroom one. The staff were super sweet and even gave me an extra slice! Also, the salad was so fresh, and that green sauce is so good that I bought a small tub to take home.\n\nLove that it’s a worker-owned co-op with a classic Berkeley feel. Their website is actually super helpful too. You can check the daily pizza/bakery menu and live music schedule before you go.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Gia S", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112963818168124326006/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhlWfkbKYgrf02Ue973PpBbHQDWls20Wvz8JhpOAqQ2RKLKB4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-04T03:23:38.123111312Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SV1JGZzRSV2N5VmxORFZ6RnRRMUJaYjJSRVNtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SV1JGZzRSV2N5VmxORFZ6RnRRMUJaYjJSRVNtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857ea1344c98af:0x314b749bfb2469c6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJr5hMNKF-hYARxmkk-5t0SzE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsVWJXMXFaM1ZWTVVoM2FXWXRVWGd3UWtWTE0zYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Unique, surprising, and delicious! Fresh, hot, and totally tasty.\nNot from the area, I was caught off guard by the 1 flavor type of pizza but we barreled ahead to enjoy what was being served. It is such a popular spot that even 30 minutes after they were open, we were already standing in a line.\n\nAll of the people who already ordered and obviously enjoying their slices were a testament to what we were about to try out. We were not disappointed! Wow.\nI never would have thought this combination would be my thing but Cheese Board pulled off an absolutely amazing topping choice. Wow.\n\nSo happy that we stopped in to try to out this spot. Also! This cola was wonderful! Who needs Coca Cola anyway? Cheese Board found an amazing replacement!\n\nAbsolutely would come back to try again :)", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Unique, surprising, and delicious! Fresh, hot, and totally tasty.\nNot from the area, I was caught off guard by the 1 flavor type of pizza but we barreled ahead to enjoy what was being served. It is such a popular spot that even 30 minutes after they were open, we were already standing in a line.\n\nAll of the people who already ordered and obviously enjoying their slices were a testament to what we were about to try out. We were not disappointed! Wow.\nI never would have thought this combination would be my thing but Cheese Board pulled off an absolutely amazing topping choice. Wow.\n\nSo happy that we stopped in to try to out this spot. Also! This cola was wonderful! Who needs Coca Cola anyway? Cheese Board found an amazing replacement!\n\nAbsolutely would come back to try again :)", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "zerofever “Isadoriana” peligrie", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110408832610720843945/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXysCbZUZAPMuJ5Z2fn5p02e-W1ULvvYO_GgpZTXFPIlgFSq1AUUg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-20T20:48:46.582001510Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsVWJXMXFaM1ZWTVVoM2FXWXRVWGd3UWtWTE0zYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsVWJXMXFaM1ZWTVVoM2FXWXRVWGd3UWtWTE0zYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857ea1344c98af:0x314b749bfb2469c6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJr5hMNKF-hYARxmkk-5t0SzE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2podE1taHhibmRhZFVjNU5tdGFXVWRVUm5oZmJVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Finally made it to the Cheese Board Pizza Collective in Berkeley — a spot I’ve wanted to try for years.\n\nThey serve one style of pizza a day, and when it’s gone, it’s gone. Today’s slice with baby chard and kale, leek, mozzarella, ricotta salata, garlic olive oil, and citrus zest was fresh, unique, and seriously good.\n\nI’m usually a simple pizza guy, but this one delivered. Absolutely worth the wait. A true Berkeley staple.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Finally made it to the Cheese Board Pizza Collective in Berkeley — a spot I’ve wanted to try for years.\n\nThey serve one style of pizza a day, and when it’s gone, it’s gone. Today’s slice with baby chard and kale, leek, mozzarella, ricotta salata, garlic olive oil, and citrus zest was fresh, unique, and seriously good.\n\nI’m usually a simple pizza guy, but this one delivered. Absolutely worth the wait. A true Berkeley staple.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mark Soehn", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108935180850097529675/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-T7Dqkb-0tUjoZTps4s7QWw8JazyzdsNcwaZfE2ewBdq032tU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-05T05:32:28.604667739Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2podE1taHhibmRhZFVjNU5tdGFXVWRVUm5oZmJVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2podE1taHhibmRhZFVjNU5tdGFXVWRVUm5oZmJVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857ea1344c98af:0x314b749bfb2469c6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJr5hMNKF-hYARxmkk-5t0SzE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psSlQzTlhSazlNVVZOcGNISjZOM0ZUU1dwUWNrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Finally got to check out this pizza place and bakery for lunch! They have a simple yet unique concept - one vegetarian pizza offered each day. I arrived right when they opened, and although there was already a line, it moved quickly. The pizza was fresh, flavorful, and beautifully simple - no frills, just quality ingredients. The green sauce paired perfectly with the pizza. I drove an hour to try it, and it was absolutely worth it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Finally got to check out this pizza place and bakery for lunch! They have a simple yet unique concept - one vegetarian pizza offered each day. I arrived right when they opened, and although there was already a line, it moved quickly. The pizza was fresh, flavorful, and beautifully simple - no frills, just quality ingredients. The green sauce paired perfectly with the pizza. I drove an hour to try it, and it was absolutely worth it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Shiny", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101958956671931411761/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLc3J5FWOgsdHTMkDDxCtDJBYYI3jy9bL5neqq7UiyDcQYIL1M=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-30T04:45:45.047392909Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psSlQzTlhSazlNVVZOcGNISjZOM0ZUU1dwUWNrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psSlQzTlhSazlNVVZOcGNISjZOM0ZUU1dwUWNrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857ea1344c98af:0x314b749bfb2469c6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJr5hMNKF-hYARxmkk-5t0SzE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4ek1VOUpkRXgxVmxVdGFUZFJlVEpxYWxWeWJGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "MUST Visit this place especially if you are a strict vegetarian. You CANNOT go wrong with their quality and hygiene. Be ready to wait for 15-20 mins in line to enjoy the pizza", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "MUST Visit this place especially if you are a strict vegetarian. You CANNOT go wrong with their quality and hygiene. Be ready to wait for 15-20 mins in line to enjoy the pizza", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Neelkanth Deshpande", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109795526046308555677/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUexCdHLb9Qp3_uXf8bA6X-CfyJzlsLOdPq2DZ81RxKz_aq7lYZMg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-16T19:10:11.060200838Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4ek1VOUpkRXgxVmxVdGFUZFJlVEpxYWxWeWJGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4ek1VOUpkRXgxVmxVdGFUZFJlVEpxYWxWeWJGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857ea1344c98af:0x314b749bfb2469c6"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJr5hMNKF-hYARxmkk-5t0SzE/photos/AWCwydi-k_CLFBanjba_jF2sAg_UO1WHYxJyS